            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h1>blender中文翻译贡献教程</h1>\n<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>因为blender cn社区的老教程已经过时许久，可能会导致不少问题，故此写一份新的版本</p>\n<p>主要内容参考<a href=\"https://docs.blender.org/manual/zh-hans/3.4/contribute/index.html\">blender docs</a>以及<a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/b1a48105e05c\">blender cn 老教程</a></p>\n<p>本教程主要针对Windows下，Mac&amp;Linux平台建议参考官方文档</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://copur.xyz/posts/blender-doc-translation\" target=\"_blank\">https://copur.xyz/posts/blender-doc-translation</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://copur.xyz/posts/blender-doc-translation",
            "title": "blender中文翻译贡献教程",
            "date_modified": "2022-08-06T10:55:28.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-10-01T05:47:02.190Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "乐得自在",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<h2>完善的文档</h2>\n<p>首先声明，这不是PE，这是用于优化wine体验的玩意</p>\n<p>首先，因为这个是内测版应用，所以wine、7z、文泉驿和容器等依赖都未实现自动安装</p>\n<p>所以第一步当然就是安装wine 7z 文泉驿啦</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://copur.xyz/posts/elwi\" target=\"_blank\">https://copur.xyz/posts/elwi</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://copur.xyz/posts/elwi",
            "title": "edgeless for Linux食用手册",
            "date_modified": "2020-05-16T21:26:28.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-10-01T05:47:02.190Z",
            "author": {
                "name": "乐得自在",
                "url": "https://valaxy.site"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>搬迁完成啦</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://copur.xyz/posts/hello-world\" target=\"_blank\">https://copur.xyz/posts/hello-world</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
