        {
            "id": "",
            "content_html": "<p>因为GitHub那边SEO问题老是难以解决，而且每次构建再上传的过程特别繁琐，因此就从github迁移到了gitlab。</p>\n<br/><p>访问 <a href=\"https://copur.xyz/posts/hugo-github-to-hexo-gitlab\" target=\"_blank\">https://copur.xyz/posts/hugo-github-to-hexo-gitlab</a> 阅读全文。</p>",
            "url": "https://copur.xyz/posts/hugo-github-to-hexo-gitlab",
            "title": "从Hugo+github迁移到hexo+gitlab",
            "date_modified": "2020-05-04T09:05:16.000Z",
            "date_published": "2024-10-01T05:47:02.190Z",
            "author": {
